headline.main: INDIAN ENVOY HERE AS QUASI-DIPLOMAT; Sir Girja Bajpai, First Agent General Sent to U.S., Comes on the President Monroe

lead_paragraph: Sir Girja Shankar Bajpai, first Agent General from India to the United States, arrived yesterday from Bombay on the President Monroe of the American President Lines, which docked at Pier 8, Hoboken.
abstract: Sir G S Bajpai lauds India's effort
